{"id": 2308, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于如何减少交流中的矛盾，你都有什么心得？", "description": "人们总是忙着思考如何反驳对方，一遍一遍重复相同的内容，我说的 X 越多，你说的 Y 也越多。（题图来自：istock ©nadia_bormotova ）", "record_count": 2202, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180427234304gGQ8RHSsvKDkumN3.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-07T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 280320, "content": "快要爆炸的时候忍住，微微一笑说一句:祝你成功?", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318881}, {"id": 280576, "content": "倾听对方，并且察觉对方与自己是否在一个维度对话，不是的话立即点出，并寻找回到同一纬度的方向", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961662}, {"id": 280321, "content": "观点不同不代表一定要争个输赢对错，随时准备接受新的思想", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275438}, {"id": 280577, "content": "听是听。说是说，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338280}, {"id": 281089, "content": "对方说的我都不反驳。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340119}, {"id": 280322, "content": "对事不对人", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276454}, {"id": 280578, "content": "不要跟不懂你的人费话!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320964}, {"id": 281858, "content": "暴力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345035}, {"id": 280323, "content": "“常与同好争高下，不与傻瓜论短长。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654432}, {"id": 280324, "content": "赢在格局，输在计较", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120405}, {"id": 280580, "content": "如果是要解决矛盾，先把自己的情绪感受缩小. 心态平和的听对方叙述。这很重要，必然都会以吵架结尾。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338284}, {"id": 282372, "content": "注意自己的心态不炸裂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346908}, {"id": 280325, "content": "对。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084495}, {"id": 280327, "content": "罗列观点 1.2.3. 不要 然后。。。就是。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715421}, {"id": 280328, "content": "都行 可以 没问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291217}, {"id": 289800, "content": "沉默是金。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386236}, {"id": 280329, "content": "设身处地", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305215}, {"id": 280585, "content": "冷静，我们是在解决问题？还是在争谁对谁错？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107517}, {"id": 284937, "content": "减少跟三观不合的人交流", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360539}, {"id": 280330, "content": "尽量用事实和数据说话的我成了单身狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919463}, {"id": 280586, "content": "人与人之间可以理解，无法感同身受，叫不醒的让他睡去吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874421}, {"id": 281098, "content": "听懂对方在说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291382}, {"id": 280331, "content": "寻求共同的利益点 而非强调自己的立场", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305215}, {"id": 280587, "content": "先等对方说完行不行 等我说的时候你别插嘴行不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338325}, {"id": 280332, "content": "不交流，冷战", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475237}, {"id": 280588, "content": "换位思考，也就是把自己也换在一个难受的位置上思考！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338324}, {"id": 280333, "content": "不要只说 不做。不要只空想 要实际行动。不要虚假 不要做假。大家都不傻！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337427}, {"id": 280589, "content": "不解释", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338327}, {"id": 280334, "content": "在反驳对方之前，先想想对方观点的由来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337431}, {"id": 280335, "content": "理解清楚对方的观点，清晰的表明自己的观点", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337435}, {"id": 280336, "content": "多站在对方的立场思考，多一些理解也多一些宽容", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180352}, {"id": 281872, "content": "不要较真", "image": "img/option/option/20180515082312bVUx8oP9yjiGkTd5", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341091}, {"id": 280337, "content": "给出清晰的定义。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724309}, {"id": 280593, "content": "肯定你自己，易于接受他人换点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303485}, {"id": 280594, "content": "注重说话内容而不是情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1309486}, {"id": 280339, "content": "任何事情都没有所谓的“正确答案”，而我们只能针对特定时间发生的事物，根据当下不违背社会道德准则以及有逻辑性的判断情况下找到所谓的“正确答案”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337440}, {"id": 280595, "content": "两人关系好就随便谈啦。关系不疏不密就不要开太多玩笑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312535}, {"id": 281620, "content": "保持镇静是首要的，心平气和讨论问题是修养，讨论问题不要无理搅三分。通情达理最能体现家教。说事儿就说事儿，多换位思考，每个人的观点角度都是不同的，谁的方法合适听谁的。以大菊为重。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285784}, {"id": 280342, "content": "别试图改变他人的看法", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201185}, {"id": 280598, "content": "是时候选择倾听和倾诉，别淤积太多", "image": "img/option/option/20180508110548giuCBcVRHxNlqJ7v.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338400}, {"id": 280343, "content": "思路一定要清楚", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269701}, {"id": 280344, "content": "实际上朋友们深藏不露，我尽力表现的幼稚但进取，希望他们多教我一点_(°ω°」∠)_", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047703}, {"id": 280346, "content": "尊重彼此，学会倾听～", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1336437}, {"id": 280348, "content": "注重对方说的内容，而不是态度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337479}, {"id": 280349, "content": "抓主要矛盾与第一目的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337470}, {"id": 282141, "content": "首先控制自己的情绪，语气比内容重要。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346180}, {"id": 280350, "content": "先看事情是否真的有必要争论吧，保留自己的意见尊重他人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482668}, {"id": 280606, "content": "有时说赢了对方听不进去，说输了对方才听得进去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248008}, {"id": 280351, "content": "矛盾不激化，冷静面对，是一个人的素养", "image": "img/option/option/20180507131555SNqnVlxW3pEMmiIu", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337477}, {"id": 280355, "content": "仔细听听对方在说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325762}]}